							<div class="text-box">
								<p class="about">The Wattles Prosperity Bible, The Law of Attraction Prosperity Bible and The Wattles Quotable Bible are published by Princeton Cambridge Publishing Group, Princeton, New Jersey.</p>

								<p class="about">Princeton Cambridge Publishing Group is the work product of Richard A. Catalina, Jr., Esq., the company’s President and CEO.  In addition to ProsperityBible.com, Princeton Cambridge Publishing Group owns and operates the Success and Personal Development web site, <a target="_blank" href="http://www.successmanual.com/" title="The Success Manual - FREE Success Ebooks - FREE Self Improvement Ebooks - Success Keys">The Success Manual</a>, at <a href="http://www.successmanual.com/">www.successmanual.com</a>.  The Success Manual is a feature-packed site, offering a<a target="_blank" href="http://www.successmanual.com/category/success-manual-downloads/" title="The Success Manual FREE Ebook Download Library Post Category - FREE Success Ebooks for Immediate Download. Published by Princeton Cambridge Publishing Group, Princeton, New Jersey, United States of America.  &copy; Copyright 2010 The Princeton Licensing Group, Princeton, New Jersey, United States of America.  All Rights Reserved. Enjoy!!"> VIRTUAL LIBRARY of FREE</a> high-quality Success Ebooks (55 FREE Ebooks at last count) for immediate download, <a target="_blank" href="http://www.successmanual.com/category/success-manual-success-keys/" title="The Success Manual SUCCESS KEYS Page: SUCCESS KEYS are concise, proven and POWERFUL Success Principles, Strategies and Mastery Moves for you to implement into your daily mental programming. SUCCESS KEYS are the fundamentals, and as you work these SUCCESS KEYS into your Thought processes, you will begin to bring about the necessary internal transformation to attain SUCCESS CONSCIOUSNESS. SUCCESS KEYS are directly based on the teachings and works of the great Masters of Success; in order to achieve Success, we must think like and model ourselves after Successful people.">Success Keys</a> and <a target="_blank" href="http://www.successmanual.com/category/success-strategist-manual-articles-laws-of-success/" title="The Success Manual SUCCESS STRATEGIES Page: The Success Strategist Manual consists of a series of thought-provoking Success based inquiries into our thinking processes. We must engage in consistent critical analyses of the Thoughts that we harbor within. Our Thoughts are the fundamental building blocks of our belief systems, conditioning, habits and paradigms. These, in turn, determine our behavior, within a true &#34;cause and effect&#34; system. Our behavior, in turn, determines our actions; and our actions, in turn, determine our results. Our results, the effects, are what we may see and perceive through our intellectual faculties, but it is our Thoughts that are the cause. Original essays will be posted on a consistent basis in the Success Strategist Manual. Read them. Study them. Understand them. Use them. Increase your level of awareness by bringing forth Growth through the Science and Art of Purposeful Thought.">Success Strategies</a> &mdash; content rich articles and posts providing valuable information crucial to attaining Health, Wealth, Prosperity and Success &mdash; and <a target="_blank" href="http://www.successmanual.com/success-beacon-free-newsletter/" title="FREE Newsletter: The SUCCESS BEACON! - Subscribe NOW. The Success Beacon! is The Success Manual's FREE informative newsletter that will provide you with compelling insights, teachings and strategies developed by the great Success Masters, Teachers and Sages that will literally TRANSFORM your " circumstance-controlled,="circumstance-controlled," "victim"=""victim"" failure="failure" consciousness="consciousness" into="into" Powerful,="Powerful," Creative="Creative" and="and" Masterful="Masterful" SUCCESS="SUCCESS" CONSCIOUSNESS!"="CONSCIOUSNESS!"">The Success Beacon newsletter</a>, an informative of material to assist your journey to be, do and have more in this Life.</p>
								<p class="about">Richard is a practicing Intellectual Property, Technology and Internet law attorney with offices in Robbinsville and Princeton, New Jersey, and New York, New York.  He has been practicing law for more than twenty years and has been named a “New Jersey Super Lawyer” for seven consecutive years (2004-2010) appearing in annual editions of <em>New Jersey</em> monthly magazine.</p>
							</div><!-- .text-box close -->
							
							<div class="text-box">
								<p align="center"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Richard A. Catalina, Jr.</span></strong></p>
								<p class="about">Richard is a life-long Student of Success and has been studying the Secrets of Success since his college days when he participated in The est Seminar Training program and became a student of yoga and meditation.  Since then, Richard has read hundreds of books on the subjects of self improvement, personal development and Success and studied materials from Anthony Robbins to Zig Ziglar.  During 2008-2009, Richard studied as a personal student under one of the greatest Success Masters and Thinkers of our modern day, Bob Proctor, and Richard's present Life philosophy as to the impact of Thought (cause) as the originator of the events and circumstances of our lives (effect) heavily reflects the teachings of Bob Proctor.</p>
								<p class="about">Richard's favorite Success books include <em>Think and Grow Rich</em> by Napoleon Hill, <em>The Greatest Salesman in the World</em> by Og Mandino, <em>Awaken the Giant Within</em> by Anthony Robbins, <em>Secrets of the Millionaire Mind</em> by T. Harv Eker, <em>The Secret of the Ages</em> by Robert Collier, <em>As a Man Thinketh</em> by James Allen and <em>The Science of Getting Rich</em> by Wallace D. Wattles.</p>

								<p class="about">In December 2009, Richard launched his own Success website,<strong> <a href="http://www.successmanual.com/">The Success Manual</a></strong>, and its companion free weekly newsletter, <strong>The Success Beacon</strong>, both of which are published by Princeton Cambridge Publishing Group.  The Success Manual features original articles, essays and other Success based references and offers<strong> <a href="http://www.successmanual.com/category/success-manual-downloads/">FREE quality Ebooks</a></strong> of history's greatest Success classics.</p>
								<p class="about">In July 2010, Richard launched his first product series, <strong>The Wattles Prosperity Bible</strong>, <strong>The Law of Attraction Prosperity Bible</strong> and <strong>The Wattles Quotable Bible</strong>, all published by Princeton Cambridge Publishing Group and available at <strong><a href="http://www.prosperitybible.com/">www.prosperitybible.com</a></strong>.</p>

								<p class="about">Richard is married and is a devoted husband and father to three beautiful children.  When not working, Richard enjoys spending time with his family.</p>
